Source: build2-staged
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Alex Syrnikov <pioneer19@mailo.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12),
 dh-exec,
 pkg-kde-tools,
 libpkgconf-dev (>= 1.6.3-5)
Standards-Version: 4.5.0
Homepage: https://build2.org/

Package: build2-staged
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: C++ Build Tool from build2 toolchain (staged version)
 build2 is an open source (Expat), cross-platform build tool from
 build2-toolchain for developing and packaging C++ code.
 This package contains build tool (b). Other tools
 (bdep, bpkg) are in build2-tools package. This is staged (in development)
 version.

Package: libbuild2-staged-<%- major_minor_version %>
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Conflicts: libbuild2-<%- major_minor_version %>
Description: shared library for build2 tool
 This package provides shared library for build2 tool.
 .
 build2 is an open source (Expat), cross-platform build tool from
 build2-toolchain for developing and packaging C++ code.
 .
 build2-toolchain is a hierarchy of tools that includes the build
 system (b-staged), package dependency manager (bpkg-staged for 
 package consumption), and project dependency manager (bdep-staged
 for project development).
 build2-toolchain provides similar functionality like
 conan+cmake+make or vcpkg+cmake+make.

